## Complete Examples

### Login Form

```html
<div id="user-login-container">
  <form id="user-login-form" action="/login" method="post">
    <h1 id="user-login-heading">Sign In</h1>
    
    <div id="user-login-email-field">
      <label for="user-email-input">Email Address</label>
      <input id="user-email-input" 
             type="email" 
             name="email"
             required
             aria-required="true">
    </div>
    
    <div id="user-login-password-field">
      <label for="user-password-input">Password</label>
      <input id="user-password-input" 
             type="password" 
             name="password"
             required
             aria-required="true">
    </div>
    
    <div id="user-login-actions">
      <button id="user-login-submit-button" type="submit">
        Sign In
      </button>
      <a id="user-password-forgot-link" href="/password/reset">
        Forgot password?
      </a>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>
```

### Article Card

```html
<article id="article-123-card" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
  <header id="article-123-header">
    <h2 id="article-123-title">
      <a id="article-123-title-link" href="/articles/123">
        Understanding Ruby on Rails
      </a>
    </h2>
    <div id="article-123-metadata">
      <span id="article-123-author">By John Doe</span>
      <time id="article-123-date" datetime="2025-11-03">
        November 3, 2025
      </time>
      <span id="article-123-reading-time">5 min read</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  
  <div id="article-123-excerpt">
    <p>Learn the basics of Ruby on Rails...</p>
  </div>
  
  <footer id="article-123-footer">
    <div id="article-123-tags">
      <span id="article-123-tag-ruby">Ruby</span>
      <span id="article-123-tag-rails">Rails</span>
    </div>
    <div id="article-123-actions">
      <a id="article-123-read-link" href="/articles/123">Read more</a>
      <button id="article-123-bookmark-button" type="button">Bookmark</button>
    </div>
  </footer>
</article>
```

### Modal Dialog

```html
<div data-controller="modal" id="delete-article-modal" class="hidden">
  <div id="delete-article-modal-overlay" 
       data-action="click->modal#close"
       data-modal-target="overlay"></div>
       
  <div id="delete-article-modal-content" 
       role="dialog"
       aria-labelledby="delete-article-modal-title"
       aria-modal="true"
       data-modal-target="content">
    
    <div id="delete-article-modal-header">
      <h2 id="delete-article-modal-title">Delete Article</h2>
      <button id="delete-article-modal-close-button"
              type="button"
              data-action="click->modal#close"
              aria-label="Close dialog">
        ×
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div id="delete-article-modal-body">
      <p>Are you sure you want to delete this article? This action cannot be undone.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div id="delete-article-modal-footer">
      <button id="delete-article-cancel-button"
              type="button"
              data-action="click->modal#close">
        Cancel
      </button>
      <button id="delete-article-confirm-button"
              type="button"
              class="bg-red-600 text-white">
        Delete Article
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```
## Quick Reference Cheat Sheet

| Element Type | ID Pattern | Example |
|--------------|------------|---------|
| Form | `[resource]-[action]-form` | `user-login-form` |
| Text Input | `[resource]-[field]-input` | `article-title-input` |
| Textarea | `[resource]-[field]-textarea` | `comment-content-textarea` |
| Select | `[resource]-[field]-select` | `article-category-select` |
| Checkbox | `[resource]-[field]-checkbox` | `user-terms-checkbox` |
| Radio | `[resource]-[field]-[value]-radio` | `visibility-public-radio` |
| Button | `[action]-button` or `[resource]-[action]-button` | `save-button`, `article-delete-button` |
| Container | `[context]-container` | `user-dashboard-container` |
| Section | `[name]-section` | `hero-section` |
| Navigation | `[context]-navigation` | `main-navigation` |
| Modal | `[purpose]-modal` | `delete-confirmation-modal` |
| Dropdown | `[context]-dropdown` | `user-menu-dropdown` |
| List | `[resource]-list-container` | `articles-list-container` |
| Card | `[resource]-card` | `article-preview-card` |
| Panel | `[purpose]-panel` | `stats-panel` |
| Link | `[context]-[page]-link` | `nav-home-link` |

